{
  "ref": "worker-the-darkfrost-",
  "categoryRef": "npc",
  "title": "Worker (The Darkfrost)",
  "sections": [
    {
      "title": "Standard dialogue",
      "sections": [
        {
          "title": "Brown hair",
          "sections": [],
          "dialogues": [
            {
              "lines": [
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Hello there!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Worker",
                  "text": "Oh, hello."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "How are things going up here?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Worker",
                  "text": "The beast still rages, but we're managing."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Worker",
                  "text": "Plenty of treasure and materials to be found in the tunnels, at least!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "What will you do with it all?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Worker",
                  "text": "The raw materials will be used to maintain Cam Torum. As for everything else, if you help us, you're allowed a share of the treasures."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "That's very generous, thank you."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "title": "Grey hair",
          "sections": [],
          "dialogues": [
            {
              "lines": [
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Hello!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Worker",
                  "text": "..."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Worker",
                  "text": "Hmm? Did you say something?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "I said hello."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Worker",
                  "text": "Oh, that's nice."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Are you okay?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Worker",
                  "text": "Why wouldn't I be? I'm not the one lost in the mountain!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Excuse me? Who's lost in the mountain?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Worker",
                  "text": "Karlo! Oh sweet Karlo... An inspiration to us all!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Worker",
                  "text": "He really knew how to swing a pickaxe, but where did that get him?!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Worker",
                  "text": "Trapped in the depths under all that rock and stone..."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "Do you think he's still alive?"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Worker",
                  "text": "I don't know."
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Worker",
                  "text": "What I do know is that I do this for Karlo. Let's make him proud!"
                },
                {
                  "speaker": "Player",
                  "text": "For Karlo!"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "dialogues": []
    },
    {
      "title": "Overhead dialogue",
      "sections": [],
      "dialogues": [
        {
          "lines": [
            {
              "speaker": "Worker",
              "text": "For Karlo!"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Worker",
              "text": "Into the tunnels, quick!"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Worker",
              "text": "Let's go!"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Worker",
              "text": "Quickly, while it's recovering!"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Worker",
              "text": "What's it left this time?"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Worker",
              "text": "It's coming back!"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Worker",
              "text": "Prepare yourselves!"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Worker",
              "text": "Retreat!"
            },
            {
              "speaker": "Worker",
              "text": "Run!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}